后向以色列提供的军事援助，以及为解救加沙哈马斯扣押的人质所做的努力</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 22:25:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-emotionally-tells-u-s-jewish-leaders-i-refuse-to-be-silent/0000018b-20a2-d010-a59f-b9e3776d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙边境的以色列军队观察员：“他们拍摄了我们的相机，我们什么也看不见”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-spotter-on-gaza-border-they-shot-our-cameras-we-couldnt-see-a-thing/0000018b-1b64-df31-a99f-7fe7fb600000</link><description>在一份录制的证词中，一名士兵讲述了她和她的朋友们如何在外面的恐怖分子试图闯入的情况下躲藏了几个小时。据她说，观察系统遭到枪击并被禁用，以防止它们被发现</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 21:05:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-spotter-on-gaza-border-they-shot-our-cameras-we-couldnt-see-a-thing/0000018b-1b64-df31-a99f-7fe7fb600000</guid></item><item><title>“真正的灵魂伴侣”在加沙附近的战场上被哈马斯枪杀——他们的家人忙着寻找答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/true-soulmates-shot-by-hamas-near-gaza-and-family-must-scrambles-for-answers/0000018b-1f4e-d465-abbb-1ffedef00000</link><description>朱迪·韦恩斯坦·哈盖 (Judi Weinstein Haggai) 打电话说，周六早上，她和她的丈夫在基布兹附近遭到枪击。接下来发生的事情尚不清楚——他们的孩子一直在向当局寻求帮助</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 20:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/true-soulmates-shot-by-hamas-near-gaza-and-family-must-scrambles-for-answers/0000018b-1f4e-d465-abbb-1ffedef00000</guid></item><item><title>拜登向以色列人发表了内塔尼亚胡永远无法发表的演讲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.highlight/biden-gave-israelis-the-speech-that-netanyahu-could-never-deliver/0000018b-1f8d-df31-a99f-7fcf0a580001</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登发表了热情洋溢、鼓舞士气的犹太复国主义演讲，而以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡却无法向他心烦意乱的国家发表这样的演讲。但这并不是给以色列政府的空白支票</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 19:22:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.highlight/biden-gave-israelis-the-speech-that-netanyahu-could-never-deliver/0000018b-1f8d-df31-a99f-7fcf0a580001</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦卫生部：3名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸村庄被蒙面定居者杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-3-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-village-by-masked-settlers/0000018b-1f43-df31-a99f-7fc316c90000</link><description>巴勒斯坦卫生部表示，另有八人受伤，被送往萨拉菲特和纳布卢斯的医院，并补充说，其中三人颈部和腹部有枪伤，情况危急</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 16:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-3-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-village-by-masked-settlers/0000018b-1f43-df31-a99f-7fc316c90000</guid></item><item><title>将战争引向哈马斯：决定以色列反应的三个关键因素</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/taking-the-war-to-hamas-three-key-factors-shaping-israels-response/0000018b-1f20-d465-abbb-1fb6e01f0000</link><description>如果政治领导人不明确目标是什么，即使是最周密的计划也会立即出错。这只是第一个问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 15:39:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/taking-the-war-to-hamas-three-key-factors-shaping-israels-response/0000018b-1f20-d465-abbb-1fb6e01f0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦能源局称加沙发电厂因缺乏燃料而停止运营</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/gaza-power-plant-stops-operating-due-to-lack-of-fuel-palestinian-energy-authority-says/0000018b-1efe-d2fc-a59f-dfff86f70000</link><description>巴勒斯坦能源管理局负责人表示，加沙燃料供应的终止是一场“灾难”，可能会产生“广泛的后果”，包括停止供水，将使医院的“恶劣条件”恶化</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 14:50:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/gaza-power-plant-stops-operating-due-to-lack-of-fuel-palestinian-energy-authority-says/0000018b-1efe-d2fc-a59f-dfff86f70000</guid></item></channel></rss>